        "description": "The solver has been verified against standard benchmark cases (lid-driven cavity, backward-facing step) with published convergence data. Internal consistency checks (mass balance residuals < 1e-5) are documented for each simulation. Gradation 2 requires benchmark verification for relevant physics — satisfied by the published solver validation suite and case-specific residual monitoring."
