      "rationale": "Validation experiments use the identical pump geometry and operating conditions as the COU, meeting Gradation 2 relevance requirements."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/factor/morrison-cou1-nse-008",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
